OL,3,C'Systemic safety issues' found at
OL,4,CDerriford Hospital after woman killed
OL,5,Cby helicopter landing
OL,7,FAn inspector has found "systemic
OL,8,Fsafety issues" in the design and
OL,9,Foperation of hospital landing sites,
OL,10,Fafter a woman died last year.
OL,12,FJean Langan, 87, was blown over while
OL,13,Fa helicopter was landing at Derriford
OL,14,FHospital, Plymouth on 4 March 2022.
OL,16,FShe was walking through Car Park B
OL,17,Fafter an appointment with her niece
OL,18,Fwhen she was hit by high levels of
OL,19,Fdownwash from a HM Coastguard
OL,20,Fhelicopter landing on the helipad
OL,21,Fabove.
